                                                                <customfield id="customfield_12310192" key="com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.customfieldtypes:textarea">
                        <customfieldname>Release Note</customfieldname>
                        <customfieldvalues>
                            <customfieldvalue>Basically the problem here is that the client gets confused, it tries to send a ping to the server but since the tcp queue is full it&amp;#39;s unable to do so. The logic responsible for sending occasional pings based on the timeout gets confused by this, and ends up flooding the server with pings. Eventually this clears up, however it can result in increased load on the server and instability for the effected client.</customfieldvalue>

